    "title": {
        "rendered": "Flexible Content Field"
    },
    "content": {
        "rendered": "<p>The Flexible Content field provides a flexible content builder interface. It allows users to create dynamic layouts by selecting from predefined content block types and arranging them in any order.</p>\n<h2>Key Features</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Dynamic layout builder</li>\n<li>Multiple layout types</li>\n<li>Drag and drop ordering</li>\n<li>Nested content structures</li>\n<li>Customizable templates</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Settings</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Layouts &#8211; Define available content block types</li>\n<li>Button Label &#8211; Customize the &#8220;Add Row&#8221; text</li>\n<li>Min/Max Layouts &#8211; Limit number of blocks</li>\n<li>Layout Settings &#8211; Configure each layout type</li>\n</ul>\n",
        "protected": false
    },
